Community Hero – AI Powered Civic Problem Solver
Problem Statement Selected
Community Hero – Hyperlocal Problem Solver

Solution Overview
The aim of the Community Hero service is to use an AI-driven platform to connect people with their local government so they can effectively resolve community issues through a seamless communication channel.

There are many civic issues faced by individuals each day in various municipalities, such as potholes, broken street lights, exposed electric wiring, leaking drains, overflowing garbage, and dangerous infrastructure for the public. Because of the frustration and lack of accountability experienced by the public due to unresolved and/or delayed issues, most residents do not know about nor do they trust the proper way to report these types of issues.

Community Hero addresses this issue through the development of a simple and comprehensive digital reporting system by which individuals can submit photos, the exact physical location, and simple descriptions of the issue they wish to resolve.

The Community Hero platform uses AI technology to:

Identify the type of issue
Determine the degree of urgency
Assess for any potential public safety concerns
Identify the appropriate department for resolution
Determine if the problem is an emergency
Assist municipalities with expediting the resolution to problems reported

By developing a digital reporting system, Community Hero provides a means for citizens and municipalities to establish a connection through a modern and user-friendly civic dashboard.

Overall, the intent of the Community Hero project team was to create a solution that would not only enable citizens to report issues and have them resolved in a timely manner, but also enable municipalities to increase productivity and improve their processes while integrating hardware and software via an AI-based workflow.

