Innovation & Impact
Community Hero is a platform that facilitates the collaborative efforts of the community through technology. It combines artificial intelligence (AI) with actual city-based processes to enhance:

- Public Safety
- Civic Transparency
- Citizen Participation
- Faster Infrastructure Response

This platform is intended to help communities establish a framework for future smart cities where AI will allow the city to be more engaging, well-organized, and friendly to its citizens.

Community Hero will enable active community involvement by making the process of reporting on community issues simpler and smarter.

